history.content:
We're a data science student organization promoting data science research, projects, and teaching! We invite you to join us in one (or more) of our 3 teams: data tinkering, infrastructure, and education. Our second info session is this Thursday (2/21) 8-9 pm at Wheeler 24.

Sign up at databears.org/join! If you have any questions, shoot us an email at recruits@db.berkeley.edu. Hope to see you all there!
